# Akvarellskiss Pigment Database - GitHub Repository

This contains the complete pigment database tool, ready for embedding in WordPress.

## Files:
- `index.html` - Main HTML structure
- `style.css` - All styling
- `script.js` - Data loading and rendering logic
- `pigments.json` - Pigment data (already in English)
- `README.md` - This file

## How to Embed in WordPress:

### Option A: HTML Block Method
1. In your WordPress editor, add an **HTML/Custom HTML block**
2. Go to this URL: `https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YOUR_REPO/artlab-pigment-database/main/index.html`
3. Copy and paste the entire file content into the block
4. Click "Update" or "Publish"

### Option B: Iframe Method (Recommended)
1. Add an **HTML iframe block** in WordPress
2. Paste this URL: `https://your-github-username.github.io/artlab-pigment-database/`
3. The full site will load in the iframe

